data.text:
@rachelle879 Hi, I am sorry to hear about the cancellation. You do not have to attach the boarding pass to make a claim. If you need further assistance, please contact our live support at: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards, 
Viktoria

@re_raw @re_raw Hi, no you can't upgrade a SAS ticket using Asiana club points. You can upgrade with money or Eurobonus points.
You can read more about it on our website https://t.co/lBHWsvXzjx
Kind regards, Mikael.

@nareik91 @nareik91 Hi, if you have a silver membership or higher, you should be able to order a new Eurobonus card via "My Eurobonus".
If it doesn't work, please contact us via our live chat or by phone so we can help you arrange this https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R
Kind regards, Mikael

@gru_mag @gru_mag Hej, jag testade precis och för mig fungerar det att logga in både i appen och på vår hemsida. Jag använder Google Chrome. Så testa gärna igen.
Skulle du fortfarande ha problem, kontakta oss via vår live chat eller telefon https://t.co/z4gOZAAJQJ
Vänlig hälsning, Mikael

@rscrase Hi, if you wish to contact our Norwegian customer service, you can reach us on +47 21 89 64 00 or our live chat which can be found here: https://t.co/cIkJt93dZ5
Kind regards,
Rebecka

@RyanProgress Hi, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. If you haven't reported your bag at the airport, please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
or call baggage service here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
Kind regards, Johanna

@returnofserve Hi, I am sorry to hear you didn't get access to Wifi, you can request a refund via our web form here: https://t.co/xMt9zSJ1AK

Kind regards,
Rebecka

@cybermazz Hi Maz
Contact us on messenger or live chat https://t.co/fxd6BsFhK5 and our customer service can help you further.
Kind regards /Anna

@IrisClasson @IrisClasson Hi, I've just checked and it works for me, both in Chrome and Safari. So please try again.
Thank you for your feedback.
Kind regards, Mikael

@MangaFried @MangaFried Hi, please contact us via Facebook Messenger, our live chat or by phone and we will help you check the information we have regarding your refund.
You can find our contact information and opening hours via this link: https://t.co/b3QIqPkF0R
Kind regards, Mikael

@lamexichic @lamexichic Hi, if you can't call, please contact us via Facebook Messenger or our live chat, our chatbot Turi will connect you to a live agent when one is available
https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards, Mikael

@lamexichic Hello! If you have further questions regarding your claim, please contact our customer service by phone, messenger or live chat. Contact information can be found here: https://t.co/b3QIqPkF0R

Kind regards,
Jenny

@wedoug @wedoug Hi, please contact us via our live chat or by phone, so we can check your booking and help you add your baggage/sport equipment.
You can find our live chat, contact information and opening hours via this link: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards, Mikael.

@bpmurray @bpmurray Hi, try clearing cache and cookies, or try a different web browser. If you use a VPN service, try to turn it off.
If this doesn't help, please contact us via our live chat or by phone and we will help you book your flight https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards, Mikael

@AddressingLife @AddressingLife Hi, unfortunately the handling time is longer than usual right now.
If you contact us via our live chat or by phone, we can check so your case is registered in our system and if it's been handled or not https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards, Mikael.

@pilip_ann Hi,
Yes that is correct.
Kind regards, Lena

@sportsf34542424 Hi,
I’m happy to hear that you had a good experience with us. We really appreciate you writing us, and I will gladly pass your feedback along.
Kind regards, Lena

@alexreid1964 Hi,
I’m so sorry to hear that you had a bad experience with us. I will pass your feedback along. Please let us know if we can help you with anything else.
Kind regards, Lena

@HagmanTrude @HagmanTrude Hi, please contact us via our live chat or by phone, so we can check which information we have regarding your case right now 
https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj We apologize for any inconvenience.
Kind regards, Mikael

@Bigtunaheyohhh @Bigtunaheyohhh Hi, if you use a VPN service, try to turn it off temporarily. If you use a public Wi-fi, try using your mobile network.
If this doesn't help, contact us via our live chat or by phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards, Mikael

@macdrodro Hi, the queues can be long when calling so keep trying or you can wait until they reach out to you which they will but please be patient, it can take longer than the 3 days you have waited.
Kind regards,
Stina

@lady_angiee Hello, please contact us by chat or phone for information regarding your refund. https://t.co/b3QIqPkF0R
Best regards,
Stina
